{
  "builds": [
    { "src": "backend.py", "use": "@vercel/python" }
  ],
  "routes": [
    { "src": "/(.*)", "dest": "backend.py" }
  ]
}
```

*(Your main file is `backend.py` based on your repo, not `main.py`)*

---

### Then update your frontend env variable

In your **frontend** Vercel project → Settings → Environment Variables:
```
NEXT_PUBLIC_API_URL=https://your-backend.vercel.app
